  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0a41b547204c34defa81f765dfe5f3d4, type: 3}
  m_Name: DemonData_Priocept
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: LSG::LSG.DemonData_Priocept
  demonName: Priocept
  canDateDemonMultipleTimes: 0
  introDialogue: '"He gives you his phone number.   It''s missing the last digit,
    but assures you it will work anyways.  His broad smile has too many teeth, his
    legs have too many ankles, but he''s cute in that ''baby deer learning to walk''
    kind of way.


    ""I''m really doing you a favor,"" he says shyly, ""sometimes
    there are gaps in reality, especially on stairs, it''s just my job to make you
    forget.""

    "'
  minimumPowerLevel: 1
  maximumPowerLevel: 15
  outcome: You forget a childhood trauma but now you are constantly taking minor
    damage (stubbing your toe)
  boon: Gain 2 Sanity
  bane: For the rest of the game, the first 1 power white card played during a summoning
    round causes -1 Sanity loss.
  boonBaneDialogue: 
  dateOutcome: '"He helps you forget your troubles while exploring the 0th floor
    of an abandoned factory.   You''d not considered Urbex for a first date, but
    the sense of adventure is really quite thrilling.


    Dinner afterwards is
    good, although you cannot remember what you had for dessert."'
